description._content: Description: The same view of Kioni Forest Station in 1927, as No. 42, showing increase growth of the trees as a result of terracing. Macgera Forest, Elevation 4,000 feet. Location: Cyprus Date: 1927 Description: The same view of Kioni Forest Hut in 1930, as No. 43. Showing still further growth of the forest trees. Machera Forest, Elevation about 4,000 feet. Location: Cyprus Date: 1930 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/698 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown.
